    <stitle>CAB: 2000, 4000, AND 8000 - REMOVE AND INSTALL - WIPER ARM</stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="IDcomponent" graphiccount="0">
        <title>WIPER ARM</title>
        <svcsubproc id="x1600701">
            <title>Remove</title>
            <para>To remove wiper arm (Item 1,
                <hotlnk document="s16007s_35.xml" xrefid="f1600748">Figure 48</hotlnk>), first disconnect washer hose
                from washer nozzle. Lift up on lock lever securing wiper arm to wiper pivot post (Item 5,
                <hotlnk document="s16007s_35.xml" xrefid="f1600748">Figure 48</hotlnk>) and pull off. Note position of
                wiper arm for installation.
            </para>
        </svcsubproc>
        <svcsubproc id="x1600702">
            <title>Install</title>
            <para>To install, push wiper arm (Item 1,
                <hotlnk document="s16007s_35.xml" xrefid="f1600748">Figure 48</hotlnk>) onto pivot post (Item 5,
                <hotlnk document="s16007s_35.xml" xrefid="f1600748">Figure 48</hotlnk>). Note position. Push lock lever
                down to lock wiper arm and connect washer hose to washer nozzle.
            </para>
        </svcsubproc>
    </svcproc>
